 /><strong>与谢娜·谢泼德 (Shaina Shepherd) 一起“超越”</strong><br /><strong>谢娜·谢泼德的《花》</strong><br /><strong>谢娜·谢泼德的《超越车轮》</strong><br /> <strong>Shaina Shepherd 和 Duff McKagan 的“支架”</strong><br /> <strong>Shaina Shepherd 和 Duff McKagan 合作的《Kick Out The Jams》（MC5 封面）</strong></p><p>在节目<a href="https://smoochforkids.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网站</a>上，乐队的表演被描述为“短暂的安可表演”。自主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-cornell">克里斯·康奈尔</a>2017 年去世以来，三位幸存成员只一起演出过两次。他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/spine-tingling-moments-chris-cornell-tribute-show-2432182">在 2019 年康奈尔大学的致敬演出中</a>一起亮相，并在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brandi-carlile-performs-soundgarden-tracks-live-with-surviving-band-members-3019633">2021 年与布兰迪·卡莱尔 (Brandi Carlile) 一起亮相</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soundgarden-audioslave-singer-chris-cornell-died-aged-52-2073457">2017年5月18日，康奈尔大学自杀身亡</a>。他今年 52 岁。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDir9yTJZoF/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" 