期的 Instagram 故事上分享了活动片段。</p><p>该活动标志着近几个月举办的最新的名人模仿比赛。 10月，当<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timothee-chalamet">蒂莫西·查拉梅 (Timothée Chalamet)</a>相似比赛在曼哈顿市中心的华盛顿广场公园举行时，相似比赛热潮开始了。 Chalamet <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/timothee-chalamet-shows-up-at-his-own-lookalike-competition-in-new-york-3806771">出人意料地出席了这次活动</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/timothee-chalamet-offers-to-pay-police-fine-incurred-by-viral-lookalike-contest-3818451">表示愿意支付警方</a>因未经许可举办活动并吸引了约 900 人参加活动而被罚款。</p><p>从那时起，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/glen-powell">格伦·鲍威尔（Glen Powell）</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/paul-mescal-lookalike-contest-takes-place-in-dublin-just-moments-before-gladiator-2-premiere-3810698">保罗·梅斯卡尔（Paul Mescal）</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zendaya">赞达亚（Zendaya）</a>等人就开始举办相似的比赛。鲍威尔以荣誉名义参加了这次竞赛，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/glen-powell-called-into-his-own-lookalike-contest-to-promise-film-cameo-to-winners-family-3815713">承诺获胜者将在他即将上映的电影中客串</a>。</p><p>德雷克（Drake）今年大部分时间都在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">与肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）争吵</a>——后者上个月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-surprise-releases-brand-new-album-gnx-listen-in-full-3815187">出人意料地发行了一张新专辑“GNX”</a> 。在他们不和的过程中，这两位说唱歌手发布了几条针对对方的言论——其中一些言论在对方的几天甚至几小时内就被删除了。 </p><figure id="attachment_3798181" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3798181" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3798181" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Drake-live@2000x1270.jpg" alt="说唱歌手德雷克在舞台上表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Drake-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Drake-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Drake-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/up